{"tid":1420984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你話：黑社會要面子，定要命？","createTime":"2019-08-06T06:30:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T07:44:05.000Z","uid":157436,"like":83,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"bca1cc07eb541f07bbc8df82c345fd7cef76f27c","tid":1420984,"uid":157436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:30:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我通常站立於和理非同最前線勇武既中間，所以我大致上理解兩邊意見同背後理念<br />\n<br />\n每次見到黑社會打到手足我地大家都好心痛，而大家打返黑社會轉頭就好心涼<br />\n<br />\n琴晚和理非同勇武激烈爭論２個主題 <br />\n1. 主動出擊定被動還擊<br />\n2. 點樣懲罰佢地班黑社會先令雙方滿意<br />\n<br />\n我明和理非係覺得如果打死人／打到殘廢，會擔心勇武太衝動、自己要負刑責、呢２個月行動會失民心等等既理由。<br />\n我都明白勇武係憤怒、覺得得返自己人先可以保護自己人、想主動出擊同保護手足、同時覺得和理非離曬地、永遠企道德高地唔理解前線。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我嘗試整理雙方立場同感受，有錯請指出，歡迎討論"},{"pid":"4cea86b31b5dc4c7cbd9dc3a3c130b8102dbc6a0","tid":1420984,"uid":157436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:33:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0dda9c8d42e5c246f9d4cae1e9e8c5ef71834a60","tid":1420984,"uid":157436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:33:32.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"81a7049422172e82474778a620d5268b9baf7366","tid":1420984,"uid":157436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:34:03.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"c4aa81218073e3d25f7e33d93b99a0ba439c1028","tid":1420984,"uid":157436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:34:18.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"556f458db6018bc51348fd00162830c6f9cbf03f","tid":1420984,"uid":300253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:34:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fb7cc5b2b2cfa34c2e7d10b76e6334a2d47c73de","tid":1420984,"uid":157436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:34:46.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"5783f5e3137223ceafa9ad16a12d39d334026598","tid":1420984,"uid":157436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite